Setting up the X - Axis, Y - Axis and Detail tab. 3

Assign the two KPI's to x-axis and y-axis of the chart and assign the make of the cars to Detail tab to show analysis based on the make of the cars.

The two KPI's of the chart : 

  • The profit margin %: This column holds the percentage profit margin of the company.
  • Total discount %.  : This column holds the percentage total discount the company made.

Steps:

  1. Drag and drop "Total Discount % "column to the x-axis tab.
  2. Drag and drop "Profit margin  % "column to the y-axis tab.
  3. Drag and drop "Make "column to the Detail tab.
